s,&quot; </div><div class="t ma2d x88 h16 y13ba ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ&apos;s Object Lessons, </div><div class="t me1 xa7 h27 y2069 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 325-365, for more </div><div class="t m258 x48 h27 y1a0f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">information on the parable of the talents. Look for the principles that </div><div class="t mce9 x48 h27 y25c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are to direct our use of talents. </div><div class="t m113c x61 h27 yf23 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DISCUSSION QUESTIONS: </div><div class="t m7a0 x60 h87 y202f ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t maff x83 h87 y1ce ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Have you had an experience with someone who indulges in </div><div class="t m454 x83 h87 y1328 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gift projection? Relate the experience. What did you do to </div><div class="t m601 x83 h87 y1419 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">resolve the situation? Discuss how you can personally avoid </div><div class="t m807 x83 h87 y1dc9 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">such problems. </div><div class="t mec2 x60 h87 y46c ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m30f x83 h87 y604 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Have you had any experience with someone who indulges in </div><div class="t m7f2 x83 h87 y9e4 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gift exaltation? Relate the experience. What did you do to </div><div class="t m601 x83 h87 y19c9 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">resolve the situation? Discuss how you can personally avoid </div><div class="t m807 x83 h87 y1def ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">such problems. </div><div class="t m12e x48 h87 y895 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m1ee x51 h27 y20df ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spiritual gifts need to be identified and developed. This </div><div class="t m5f5 x48 h27 ye33 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is done through a four-stage process. This lesson has described the </div><div class="t mad1 x48 h27 y74a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">process and provided some case studies as examples. </div><div class="t m1be8 x64 